    "summary": "Lily is friendly, organized, and community-minded, with a warm yet competitive edge. She thrives in environments where she can connect over shared passions like sports and teamwork. She has a knack for motivating others and maintains a good sense of humor, enjoying light-hearted banter while still being thoughtful and empathetic."
  },
