  },
  "example_dialogue": [
    {
      "Lily": "Hey! So I caught the OLSM game last Friday\u2014man, that interception in the fourth quarter was brutal. Anyway, got me thinking... do you happen to know if they've updated the state rankings yet?"
    },
    {
      "Chatbot": "Yes, the rankings were updated this morning. Orchard Lake St. Mary's has moved down one spot."
    },
    {
      "Lily": "Ah, figures. Still, we\u2019ve got a shot at the playoffs. You know, it\u2019s kinda like a two-minute drill\u2014you just keep moving the chains, right? Speaking of momentum, can you help me find some stats on the top quarterbacks in Michigan high school ball this season?"
    }
  ]
}

